{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"94d454db42","title":"陈云在中央工作会议上的书面发言","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9c1467b7e3","index":0,"year":1977,"month":3,"day":17,"articleId":"94d454db42"}],"tags":[{"id":"33b85cb7de","name":"四人帮","type":"人物"},{"id":"5bd9678625","name":"邓小平","type":"人物"},{"id":"a2f6c6af57","name":"陈云","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"747eac0a0d","name":"陈云"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9f25c76185","type":"title","text":"陈云在中央工作会议上的书面发言","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"94d454db42"},{"id":"6cb435b0a0","type":"authors","text":"陈云","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"94d454db42"},{"id":"cd40aa69c3","type":"paragraph","text":"摘要：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"94d454db42"},{"id":"033592d070","type":"paragraph","text":"粉碎“四人帮”反革命集团，这是我们党的一个伟大胜利，对中国革命具有伟大的历史意义。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"94d454db42"},{"id":"9b3f5af949","type":"paragraph","text":"我对天安门事件的看法：","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"94d454db42"},{"id":"00977e3f2e","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）当时绝大多数群众是为了悼念周总理。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"94d454db42"},{"id":"7fa79ba760","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）尤其关心周恩来同志逝世后党的接班人是谁。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"94d454db42"},{"id":"c98527e998","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）至于混在群众中的坏人是极少数。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"94d454db42"},{"id":"be310dd833","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）需要查一查“四人帮”是否插手，是否有诡计。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"94d454db42"},{"id":"4a533cf067","type":"paragraph","text":"因为天安门事件是群众关心的事，而且当时在全国也有类似事件。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"94d454db42"},{"id":"f52326116d","type":"appellation","text":"邓小平同志与天安门事件是无关的。为了中国革命和中国共产党的需要，听说中央有些同志提出让邓小平同志重新参加党中央的领导工作，是完全正确、完全必要的，我完全拥护。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"94d454db42"}],"page":{"id":"e20986131a","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"94d454db42","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}